---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<Layout
  metadata={{
    title: 'TapRebook Reception — WhatsApp AI receptionist for clinics',
    description:
      'Cut no-shows by 20–40% with automated reminders, self-rescheduling, late-arrival handling, and post-visit follow-ups.',
  }}
>
  <section class="py-12 md:py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight dark:text-white">
      WhatsApp AI receptionist for clinics
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 max-w-3xl">
      TapRebook Reception reduces no-shows, speeds up scheduling & rescheduling, and frees your front desk from
      routine messaging—so staff can focus on in-person care.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-6 flex gap-3">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/contact/">Book a 10-min demo</a>
      <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="https://wa.me/91XXXXXXXXXX">WhatsApp us</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-10 border-t border-slate-200/50 dark:border-slate-800/60">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold dark:text-white">Top outcomes</h2>
    <ul class="mt-4 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
      <li class="card p-5">
        <h3 class="font-semibold">Fewer no-shows</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Smart reminders + self-rescheduling reduce missed visits by 20–40%.</p>
      </li>
      <li class="card p-5">
        <h3 class="font-semibold">Less front-desk load</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">AI handles routine chats; staff only manages exceptions.</p>
      </li>
      <li class="card p-5">
        <h3 class="font-semibold">Measurable ops</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">See completions, drop-offs, and outcomes in one place.</p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="py-10 border-t border-slate-200/50 dark:border-slate-800/60">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold dark:text-white">How it works</h2>
    <ol class="mt-4 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
      <li class="card p-5">
        <h3 class="font-semibold">1) Inquire</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Patient messages your WhatsApp number or taps a link/QR.</p>
      </li>
      <li class="card p-5">
        <h3 class="font-semibold">2) Assist</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">AI guides booking, rescheduling, reminders, and FAQs.</p>
      </li>
      <li class="card p-5">
        <h3 class="font-semibold">3) Complete</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Confirmations, follow-ups, and reviews—staff handle exceptions.</p>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </section>

  <section class="py-10 border-t border-slate-200/50 dark:border-slate-800/60">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold dark:text-white">What’s included</h2>
    <ul class="mt-4 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
      <li class="card p-5">
        <h3 class="font-semibold">Smart reminders</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Confirmations, nudges, late-arrival handling, and auto follow-ups.</p>
      </li>
      <li class="card p-5">
        <h3 class="font-semibold">Self-service rescheduling</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Patients can change time slots without calling the clinic.</p>
      </li>
      <li class="card p-5">
        <h3 class="font-semibold">Escalation to staff</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">One click to hand off to a human for edge cases.</p>
      </li>
      <li class="card p-5">
        <h3 class="font-semibold">Reports & audit trail</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Track message templates, delivery, opt-ins, and outcomes.</p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="py-12 border-t border-slate-200/50 dark:border-slate-800/60">
    <div class="md:flex items-center justify-between">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold dark:text-white">Ready to keep your schedule full?</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Start with Reception. Add Labs, Pharma and more later.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-6 md:mt-0 flex gap-3">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/contact/">Book a 10-min demo</a>
        <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/pricing/">See pricing</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
